{"title":"拿起武器来！——纪念抗日战争胜利二十周年诗笺一束","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":8,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿起武器来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——纪念抗日战争胜利二十周年诗笺一束"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿起武器来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山有号响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——反攻！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——反攻！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树树有雷响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——冲锋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——冲锋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看“星星之火”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成了长虹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看“名将之花”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落在“我”手中。〔注〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看万壑千峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烽火处处红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿起武器来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——战士！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——弟兄！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展翅高飞吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——山鹰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——山风！ 〔注〕所谓“名将之花”，是日本法西斯的一位中将，名叫阿部中将。反扫荡战斗中，被我八路军晋察冀一分区部队打死。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行军乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长空一支箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——雪山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山中一乐园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——茅舍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈火阵阵飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——赤胆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地雷轰轰响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——阻击战。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读完了一遍；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬起头来看——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曙光已在前面！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撒给炮楼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——诗传单"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫笑我着布衫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有烈火照心间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫笑我庄稼汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛著使我登高山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫笑我没炸弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“独脚牛”照样会叫唤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫你下楼来“会餐”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火烧炮楼看你团团转。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今晚我到壕沟边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕野外北风吹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪上眠冰上站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国对我笑开颜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我迎着朝霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在最前线！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕“独脚牛”，边区自造，它是抗日时期边区游击队员用的短枪，每次只装一颗子弹，人称“独脚牛”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城南庄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六三年，我又回到阜平抗战老根据地，重访城南庄，看见毛主席住过的房子，仍有弹痕留在室内一根木柱上。我不禁默诵主席写的这样的诗句：“当年鏖战急，弹洞前村壁。装点此关山，今朝更好看。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血染胭脂河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火烧城南庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千次百次，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左冲右撞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是鬼子来“扫荡”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硝烟四起雾茫茫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太行山呵山高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胭脂河呵水长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羊角声声唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铜锣阵阵响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗日到底胜利了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山里人们多欢畅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的领袖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路过城南庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他唤羊倌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又叫村长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐在那杨树下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起来话家常。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时百万雄师，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正伏在战船上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要跨黄河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要过长江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东同志的号令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也已飞出城南庄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胭脂河，英雄河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城南庄，老山乡；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条长街，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路白杨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住在村边上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席和老乡亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有甘有苦一同尝；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌机胆敢追来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪弹打进门窗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是铁打的太行山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挡住历史上所有的风浪。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}